snippet.title: EAS Child Abduction Emergency (AMBER Alert) Hondo, Texas (San Antonio) NOAA Weather Radio
snippet.description:
BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
Relayed by National Weather Service Houston/Galveston TX
931 PM CST Tue Dec 21 2021

...AMBER ALERT...

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THE MEDINA COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE IS SEARCHING FOR LUCAS WRIGHT,
WHITE, MALE, 9 YEARS OLD, 4 FEET 5 INCHES, 70 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR,
HAZEL EYES, AND WEARING ALL GREEN OUTERWEAR, LL BEAN
ORANGE/BLUE/WHITE UNDER-COAT, GRAY ADIDAS SHOES WITH RED BOTTOMS.

THE MEDINA COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE IS SEARCHING FOR ARIANA WRIGHT,
WHITE, FEMALE, 8 YEARS OLD, 4 FEET 5 INCHES, 70 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR,
HAZEL EYES, AND WEARING ALL GREEN OUTERWEAR, LL BEAN PURPLE
UNDER-COAT, BROWN BOOTS WITH A CAMO LEAF TOP.

THE MEDINA COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE IS SEARCHING FOR JONATHAN
WRIGHT, WHITE, MALE, 11 YEARS OLD, 4 FEET 8 INCHES, 80 POUNDS, BROWN
HAIR, BROWN EYES, AND WEARING ALL GREEN OUTERWEAR, LL BEAN BRIGHT
BLUE UNDER-COAT, GRAY ADIDAS SHOES WITH RED BOTTOMS.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR JONATHAN ALEXANDER WRIGHT, WHITE, MALE, 40
YEARS OLD, 5 FEET 9 INCHES, 170 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, BROWN EYES AND
POSSIBLY WEAING A GREEN JACKET OR HOODIE, IN CONNECTION WITH THEIR
ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM AT 3:45 PM ON DECEMBER 20, 2021 NEAR
CR 366 AND FM 2676 IN HONDO, TX ON FOOT.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THESE CHILDREN TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER. 

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE MEDINA
COUNTY SHERIFF'S OFFICE AT 8 3 0 7 4 1 6 1 5 3.
